// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1742 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: df5ce9a6-c6b3-57c8-a507-b224bf85ef62

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:7*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.10*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:13.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:13.10*")
